flowRoot.flowPara: It’s day 5 of our expedition, and things have been getting a little weird. I’m hearing voices in the winds. I know it sounds crazy but I can’t shut them out of my head. It sounds like little girls screaming for help. I need to know what is happening. I can’t talk to the other guys because they clearly aren’t hearing them and I don’t want them to think I’m going insane.

We followed the voices to the ravine, and tucked in the back of the ravine was a cave, going deeper into the ravine the voices got louder. I’m writing this before we go into the cave so if anything happens you will know where we were and what we were thinking. Here goes nothing...

Turns out I wasn’t the only one hearing voices, a few of the other guys came up to me when I was listening to the wind. They asked me if I heard them too. We started brainstorming about what it could be, maybe a cave was catching the wind in just the right way? Whatever it is, it’s scaring the hell out of us. We decided we’d go out tonight while the other guys are sleeping and follow them to their source. There’s a ravine near where we are sleeping and if there’s a cave making the whistling, it’d be in there...
